rComments: I would highly recommend taking this class. I learned a lot of valuable information about entrepreneurship and valuable resources that I never knew about before. Prof Orser is a good lecture speaker and I enjoyed listening to what she had to say. I found that she was a fair marker. Pay attention in class and do the important readings and ur good!
